40
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:16,720
Friday,

41
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:19,616
isn't there a greenhouse in the yard?

42
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,360
There's a tree in there.

43
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:23,880
It's an orange tree that I
planted with my father and mother

44
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:25,752
when I was little.

45
00:02:26,750 --> 00:02:29,881
My father gave my mother
this orange necklace because

46
00:02:29,881 --> 00:02:31,788
she loves oranges.

47
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:35,880
He said that the orange symbolizes

48
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:40,716
the only precious being in one's heart.

49
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,360
So romantic.

50
00:02:45,910 --> 00:02:47,842
You really sound like a human

51
00:02:48,110 --> 00:02:49,802
