52
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,432
But this kind of romance

53
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:01,068
is not for everyone.

54
00:03:01,550 --> 00:03:03,080
(Is he talking about himself?)

55
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:05,630
(Did his relationship
with the pretty sister go wrong?)

56
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:07,440
I've identified
that you're a bit down right now.

57
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:10,404
When you're down,
you need to go for a walk.

58
00:03:11,670 --> 00:03:13,398
You can even tell this?

59
00:03:14,030 --> 00:03:17,270
It seems that your observation skills
are quite strong.

60
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,190
Let's go.

61
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:21,710
Just in time,
I want to take you somewhere.

62
00:03:32,830 --> 00:03:34,522
Are we going in?

63
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,320
Aren't I prohibited from entering?

64
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:43,024
You're a cutie now so
I've decided to let you in.

65
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:07,288
It's so beautiful here.

66
00:04:08,830 --> 00:04:10,954
I have the fondest memories here.

67
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:15,428
Especially, this orange tree.

68
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:22,108
It was such a small sapling in the past.

69
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:23,880
It's so big now.

70
00:04:25,110 --> 00:04:28,398
This shows how well your
master has taken care of it.

71
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,560
You should perform well too.

72
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:35,200
I will also take good care of you.

73
00:04:49,510 --> 00:04:50,510
Mr. Lu,

74
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:56,796
do you sometimes feel that
you are as lonely as this tree?

75
00:04:58,830 --> 00:05:00,810
I don't know why

76
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:04,268
but I seem to have become
a bit different.

77
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:07,540
Yes, you've become different.

78
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:12,400
Then what do you think
is different about me?

79
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,740
Even you can't figure it out.

80
00:05:38,550 --> 00:05:39,550
Your...

81
00:05:40,550 --> 00:05:42,482
your eyes have become different.

82
00:05:44,230 --> 00:05:46,640
There's anticipation in your eyes.

83
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:49,480
The anticipation of building
a close relationship with someone.

84
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:52,996
Simply put, you want to make friends!

85
00:05:55,070 --> 00:05:56,510
Do you really think so?

86
00:05:57,640 --> 00:06:01,756
Is that really what I think?

87
00:06:03,790 --> 00:06:04,830
(Silly.)

88
00:06:04,830 --> 00:06:06,600
(Everyone needs a friend.)

89
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:09,144
(It's just that no one has ever told you.)

90
00:06:13,270 --> 00:06:14,270
You know,

91
00:06:18,350 --> 00:06:20,990
I've been used to this kind of life
long ago.

92
00:06:23,230 --> 00:06:24,670
Because of this disease,

93
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:30,050
I can't even be like a normal person,

94
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:33,160
let alone have a close relationship.

95
00:06:35,230 --> 00:06:37,210
What's the disease that you have?

96
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:52,484
It's a very complicated
and intractable disease

97
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:56,360
that can kill me if I'm not careful.

98
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,440
It's not a normal disease.

99
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:06,852
It

100
00:07:08,550 --> 00:07:10,230
is a very special allergy.

101
00:07:10,670 --> 00:07:13,178
H-How special is it?

102
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:23,648
In the extreme case of the allergy,
I will...

103
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:42,186
I will...

104
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:53,384
How can a robot be startled too?

105
00:07:54,550 --> 00:07:56,320
You have a lot of emotions.

106
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:58,600
I'll tell Fu Yang to cancel
your emotions later.

107
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,271
Okay, Mr. Lu.

108
00:07:59,271 --> 00:08:00,640
You better do it.

109
00:08:00,640 --> 00:08:02,040
Anyway, that's it.

110
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,480
You'd better not have any human contact,

111
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,000
let alone any close relationships.

112
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,790
Have you been hurt in a relationship?

113
00:08:06,790 --> 00:08:07,880
Poor boy.

114
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:09,350
I have not.

115
00:08:09,350 --> 00:08:10,550
Yes, yes, you have not.

116
00:08:10,550 --> 00:08:11,810
You have not.

117
00:08:12,230 --> 00:08:14,270
Right, back to the point.

118
00:08:14,270 --> 00:08:17,720
My disease must be kept a secret,
especially from the outside world.

119
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:20,110
I told you because I see you as a friend.

120
00:08:20,110 --> 00:08:21,720
Miss Kang Li'er doesn't know either?

121
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,740
She doesn't know.

122
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,230
Why did you mention Li'er?

123
00:08:26,230 --> 00:08:27,390
According to Friday's analysis,

124
00:08:27,390 --> 00:08:30,270
your changes these days
are related to Miss Kang.

125
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,440
Is that so?

126
00:08:33,230 --> 00:08:34,080
Think about it.

127
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:38,148
Did she say or do
anything that provoked you?

128
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:45,744
She...

129
00:08:47,350 --> 00:08:49,320
She said she wants to marry me.

130
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:51,144
It did give me a fright.

131
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:53,840
We've known each other since childhood.

132
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:56,150
When it comes to candidates for a friend,

133
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:58,406
she's the only one in the world.

134
00:08:58,590 --> 00:08:59,706
Friend?

135
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:01,720
Then think about it.

136
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:06,292
Do you have any other feelings
for her besides being friends?

137
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,448
What other feelings?

138
00:09:10,590 --> 00:09:12,558
For example,

139
00:09:13,230 --> 00:09:15,110
when you don't see her,

140
00:09:15,110 --> 00:09:17,280
your heart becomes restless,
as if there's grass growing inside.

141
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:20,400
But when you see her, you
will suddenly feel at ease

142
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:23,100
and the whole world
seems to have disappeared.

143
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:29,840
It's like you two are lying on a
soft lawn on a nice afternoon.

144
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:32,640
You suddenly feel that
there is no rush to do anything

145
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:34,590
and no rush to see anyone.

146
00:09:34,590 --> 00:09:36,150
Everything is comfortable.

147
00:09:36,150 --> 00:09:38,502
It's as if time stood still.

148
00:10:05,880 --> 00:10:08,424
It seems to be like this.

149
00:10:08,640 --> 00:10:10,272
Not wanting to do anything.

150
00:10:11,350 --> 00:10:12,754
That's the feeling.

151
00:10:13,230 --> 00:10:14,682
What's that feeling?

152
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:17,910
If you don't know what the
feeling is, you should go to her...

153
00:10:17,910 --> 00:10:18,910
Go to her?

154
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:20,640
Yes.

155
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:29,590
Isn't Miss Kang your
only human friend anyway?

156
00:10:29,590 --> 00:10:32,590
Just let her feel your dependence on her.

157
00:10:32,590 --> 00:10:33,960
Meet up with her more often.

158
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:36,840
When you are free, you can
share your daily life with each other.

159
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:39,528
Then you will become closer gradually.

160
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,000
Dependence...

161
00:10:45,590 --> 00:10:47,690
Maybe it's because of this disease,

162
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:51,320
I'm always trying
to keep a little distance from her.

163
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:55,080
Mr. Lu, I think you need to
stop thinking about your disease.

164
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:57,000
Look at how natural you
act when you're with me.

165
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:59,400
You can also do the same with Miss Kang.

166
00:11:01,110 --> 00:11:03,030
So what should I do?

167
00:11:06,470 --> 00:11:08,760
I think the eyes are very important.

168
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:12,108
First, you have to look into her eyes.

169
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,590
For example, you should have a gentle

170
00:11:15,590 --> 00:11:17,960
and determined look in your eyes.

171
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:21,608
This will make her
feel comfortable and secure too.

172
00:11:52,110 --> 00:11:54,450
The ingredients I ordered have arrived.

173
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:57,272
Mr. Lu, wait for me!

174
00:12:41,350 --> 00:12:42,370
(Please come in.)

175
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:55,580
What brings you here?

176
00:12:58,110 --> 00:12:59,440
I came to see you.

177
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:01,440
People say you look great at work.

178
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:03,240
Now I see, that's indeed true.

179
00:13:04,910 --> 00:13:07,200
The gossip about me will probably circulate
in the company

180
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:10,464
for some time now that you, the big
beauty, have come to the company.

181
00:13:11,150 --> 00:13:13,320
You can't be such a smooth talker.

182
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:16,520
I guess I'll have to teach
you how to attract girls.

183
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:18,030
No need for that, my sister.

184
00:13:18,030 --> 00:13:21,350
You know, I'm not interested in dating.

185
00:13:21,350 --> 00:13:23,880
Besides, other girls can't attract me

186
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:26,904
when a beautiful woman like you
is by my side.

187
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:30,670
Oh right.

188
00:13:30,670 --> 00:13:32,710
Would you like some tea or coffee?

189
00:13:33,150 --> 00:13:34,110
I'll pass.

190
00:13:34,110 --> 00:13:36,871
Don't you want to see
what I've got for you?

191
00:13:38,470 --> 00:13:41,674
Why did you prepare a gift
when you're just visiting me here?

192
00:13:42,030 --> 00:13:44,394
But I didn't prepare anything for you

193
00:13:44,520 --> 00:13:46,400
because you came all of a sudden.

194
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:47,400
How about this?

195
00:13:47,790 --> 00:13:49,440
Tell me what you want.

196
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:50,640
I'll give it to you.

197
00:13:51,030 --> 00:13:52,350
Really?

198
00:13:52,350 --> 00:13:53,710
I've already thought about it.

199
00:13:53,710 --> 00:13:54,970
Are you free tonight?

200
00:13:55,550 --> 00:13:57,422
Yes, of course!

201
00:13:57,790 --> 00:13:59,960
Then let's go to Lu Sen's house for dinner.

202
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:01,304
I've already told him.

203
00:14:04,880 --> 00:14:05,880
Are you sure

204
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:12,440
you want me to go to his house
for dinner with you?

205
00:14:24,350 --> 00:14:25,610
Crayfish?

206
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:29,840
Inspired by you, I
remembered that Li'er said

207
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:33,000
she couldn't find authentic crayfish
when she was studying abroad.

208
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:36,696
So I'm going to make her a crayfish dish.

209
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,590
There are many flavors of crayfish.

210
00:14:39,590 --> 00:14:43,350
There are spicy crayfish,
stir-fried crayfish, garlic crayfish,

211
00:14:43,350 --> 00:14:44,694
and 13-spice crayfish.

212
00:14:45,910 --> 00:14:48,520
The 13-spice one then.

213
00:14:48,520 --> 00:14:50,140
Li'er can't eat spicy food.

214
00:14:53,350 --> 00:14:54,350
Okay.

215
00:14:54,760 --> 00:14:55,816
Get cracking.

216
00:14:58,470 --> 00:14:59,910
Do I have to wash all these?

217
00:14:59,910 --> 00:15:01,590
Do you expect me to wash it?

218
00:15:16,520 --> 00:15:17,520
Friday,

219
00:15:17,910 --> 00:15:20,694
you look like a human when you're scared.

220
00:15:22,470 --> 00:15:26,960
I'm programmed to tremble and scream

221
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:29,030
at multilegged animals and insects.

222
00:15:29,030 --> 00:15:31,730
I think that's what you meant
by being scared.

223
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:37,172
Why does this Fu Yang always
give you these sorts of functions?

224
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:46,436
Is this Team Alpha?

225
00:15:46,760 --> 00:15:48,140
Come here for a moment.

226
00:15:51,280 --> 00:15:53,440
Wash these crayfish.

227
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:57,960
I'll ask the butler to give you
double the amount you've washed.

228
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:05,884
Let's go, Friday.

229
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:17,080
Let's begin.

230
00:17:55,455 --> 00:17:57,315
Why are you so good at cooking?

231
00:17:57,945 --> 00:17:59,805
Because I grew up eating alone.

232
00:18:00,215 --> 00:18:02,915
Have you cooked your own food
since childhood?

233
00:18:04,905 --> 00:18:06,135
Not exactly.

234
00:18:06,135 --> 00:18:09,219
At first, I could only eat
instant noodles.

235
00:18:10,855 --> 00:18:13,705
But then I got really tired of them
so I made my own meals.

236
00:18:13,705 --> 00:18:15,517
It was a difficult process

237
00:18:15,735 --> 00:18:17,115
but I couldn't help it.

238
00:18:17,785 --> 00:18:20,305
I just couldn't eat
other people's cooking.

239
00:18:22,305 --> 00:18:24,793
Friday, help me get... Master,

240
00:18:24,945 --> 00:18:26,505
it has been tough for you.

241
00:18:28,705 --> 00:18:31,705
(Something seems to have sprouted
in my heart again.)

242
00:18:31,705 --> 00:18:34,249
How did you grow up then?

243
00:18:36,375 --> 00:18:37,671
I then found out

244
00:18:38,065 --> 00:18:41,945
that premium ingredients don't
need to be cooked too much.

245
00:18:41,945 --> 00:18:44,573
So it's fine
as long as you have the money.

246
00:18:45,735 --> 00:18:46,975
(Sure enough, your happiness)

247
00:18:46,975 --> 00:18:48,715
(is beyond my understanding.)

248
00:19:03,945 --> 00:19:06,238
Friday, come and help me choose a suit.

249
00:19:12,185 --> 00:19:16,305
Master, I think that if you
really don't know what to wear,

250
00:19:16,305 --> 00:19:19,474
you should think about what
kind of style Miss Kang likes.

251
00:19:22,065 --> 00:19:24,129
Li'er did give me a suit.

252
00:19:33,255 --> 00:19:34,255
This one.

253
00:19:36,665 --> 00:19:38,705
This one really suits you!

254
00:19:38,705 --> 00:19:40,305
Miss Kang Li'er really has a good eye.

255
00:19:40,305 --> 00:19:42,597
Master will look great in it!

256
00:19:44,905 --> 00:19:47,785
Although I, your master,
look good in everything,

257
00:19:47,785 --> 00:19:50,305
I've decided to take your advice.

258
00:19:50,305 --> 00:19:51,505
I'll just wear this.

259
00:19:51,825 --> 00:19:52,665
Yes, yes.

260
00:19:52,665 --> 00:19:54,255
Master, you look good in everything.

261
00:19:54,255 --> 00:19:56,215
Hurry up and get yourself dressed up.

262
00:19:56,215 --> 00:19:58,688
I'll go down and see
what else is missing.

263
00:20:06,255 --> 00:20:06,826
(What a fool.)

264
00:20:06,826 --> 00:20:09,025
(You don't know
how to please a woman at all.)

265
00:20:09,025 --> 00:20:10,425
(Without my help, )

266
00:20:10,425 --> 00:20:12,765
(you'd really be destined to be alone.)

267
00:20:28,690 --> 00:20:30,090
♪ On the raging waves ♪

268
